{"tid":914403,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"【Claim 旅遊保】突然天氣轉冷，搞到要買件羽絨。","createTime":"2018-11-24T08:44:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-26T15:44:47.000Z","uid":37661,"like":6,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f02e8c914fe04ad59ca66dd76d5926fcc8f7bb45","tid":914403,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T08:44:50.000Z","msg":"今朝飛釜山，明明之前話呎幾日好天架。<br />\n<br />\n降落後都仲好好天既。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fsTdu1s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfsTdu1s.jpg&h=f21ae8fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WxUszt9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWxUszt9.jpg&h=e231ac5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NXJXWHv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNXJXWHv.jpg&h=c081357c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知轉個頭，無晒太陽，鳩咁撚凍，自己着嗰件外套，我見人哋香港廿度都係着佢，咁呢度得番幾度邊夠暖，焗着去買件羽絨，洗大千幾蚊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NapszuD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNapszuD.jpg&h=b9fbffa8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次去機張市場食松葉蟹，唔知咩原因，啲蟹貴晒，上次人哋開價俾我5萬，我無還價都又送雪蟹同汽水，今次開我成九萬，講到牙血都出都無上次咁平。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oXwVJmt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoXwVJmt.jpg&h=10097af7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都準備返去同保險公司 Claim 番件褸錢同隻蟹差價，仲有頭先由機張市場返 Hostel ，唔記得有架平車可以返去，結果坐咗架 1700 won 嘅貴車，我都決定要 Claim 埋佢。"},{"pid":"6d4a7e5e3b2baefe41e05c7f9b73f3f3b57e3a34","tid":914403,"uid":37661,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T08:47:13.000Z","msg":"仲有呀，釜山啲找換店個 rate 垃圾到仆街，同首爾明洞爭成截，唔知有無得可以 claim 埋差額。<br />\n<br />\n撳機連手續費都靚過找換店，但都同明洞爭好遠。"},{"pid":"b43e334bcb0dd1b4131034bd7dc28a5ed5e33adc","tid":914403,"uid":65328,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T13:29:06.000Z","msg":"負評果班唔知樓主曲線"},{"pid":"d34c18f5de63928cf16aeccf667c2142818980de","tid":914403,"uid":37661,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b43e334bcb0dd1b4131034bd7dc28a5ed5e33adc","tid":914403,"uid":65328,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T13:29:06.000Z","msg":"負評果班唔知樓主曲線"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T13:58:44.000Z","msg":"無所謂啦，得咁少負評！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今日又去番同一間嘢，坐番同一個位。<br />\n<br />\n驚俾人話舊相，加埋今日臺灣新聞落去。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/25/215002_b7c14d92fb6c4813c57f8e2710c52d79.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F25%2F215002_b7c14d92fb6c4813c57f8e2710c52d79.jpg&h=08ebf6f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日被店鋪門外大叔認得我，今日唔使講價，直接用噚日個價捉隻蟹同啲扇貝仔。<br />\n<br />\n今日仲送多罐可樂俾我，五個月前食嗰次都送個一次。<br />\n<br />\n仲要食食下，老闆娘又送個麵嚟，心諗，我今朝出門前仲食咗幾件隔夜炸雞，今日冇噚日咁肚餓喎。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/25/215109_a232b439c64e7a5206f257ab7b3e2b5d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F25%2F215109_a232b439c64e7a5206f257ab7b3e2b5d.jpg&h=95e3f007&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/25/215113_c4fab18609df919866fd00f7ea0c5bdc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F25%2F215113_c4fab18609df919866fd00f7ea0c5bdc.jpg&h=594ec565&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/25/215116_a0bb3f11ad9643b8c42442de995fbda0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F25%2F215116_a0bb3f11ad9643b8c42442de995fbda0.jpg&h=c40c99fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/25/215119_f2a420d4a871dd4017d0b77a6bbc3ee8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F25%2F215119_f2a420d4a871dd4017d0b77a6bbc3ee8.jpg&h=d2ed1ce2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然埋單就冇收送嘅嘢錢。<br />\n<br />\n走嗰陣，門口大叔仲同我握手，雖然我都唔知佢講乜。"},{"pid":"540c4f322dccf017b57a2b155fa4ecef861860c1","tid":914403,"uid":54812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T01:22:14.000Z","msg":"杯面咁嘅色嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ade4d0e619f8a0905fec21b2eef62318d742dc4c","tid":914403,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"540c4f322dccf017b57a2b155fa4ecef861860c1","tid":914403,"uid":54812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T01:22:14.000Z","msg":"杯面咁嘅色嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T01:25:09.000Z","msg":"似係辛辣麵嗰類<br />\n<br />\n啲人問我係咪咖喱公仔麵。<br />\n<br />\n都唔明啲韓國人真係食好多嘢。<br />\n<br />\n一人一隻蟹，啲乜小碟又清晒，又叫拉麵食，蟹蓋仲炒埋飯都食得晒。"},{"pid":"f17c94246082883ca85d0a744787d81eec9f0edb","tid":914403,"uid":53466,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T01:26:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"33266d1066e88d8c42eb4991bfecbc872f5feaf0","tid":914403,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f17c94246082883ca85d0a744787d81eec9f0edb","tid":914403,"uid":53466,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"b43e334bcb0dd1b4131034bd7dc28a5ed5e33adc","tid":914403,"uid":65328,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T13:29:06.000Z","msg":"負評果班唔知樓主曲線"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T01:26:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T01:54:57.000Z","msg":"泡菜國 post , 梗係負評啦！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2500063d72dd08c2d3d70f6f963576d1fcb095a5","tid":914403,"uid":44323,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"b43e334bcb0dd1b4131034bd7dc28a5ed5e33adc","tid":914403,"uid":65328,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T13:29:06.000Z","msg":"負評果班唔知樓主曲線"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T01:56:40.000Z","msg":"曲得黎唔好笑咪負評囉死蠢"},{"pid":"09e94fa54dc400b878be1ab3626f0fd9342c01f3","tid":914403,"uid":37661,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T02:33:04.000Z","msg":"香港直航去釜山嘅航空公司唔多，除咗時間爛嘅 UO , 就係釜山航空。<br />\n<br />\n釜山航空喺香港冇得網上 check in , 一定要去櫃檯拎登機證，  check in 櫃檯只在飛機起飛前兩個半鐘頭先開，即係呢班機要夜晚十一點半後先可以 check in ，早去都冇用。<br />\n<br />\n呢班機都有幾個旅行團，十一點半就排晒大隊，班團友趕住 Check in 寄行李。<br />\n<br />\n班機準時飛，飛到巡航高度就熄燈，釜山航空半廉航，冇餐派，大家可以安心瞓覺。<br />\n<br />\n註：釜山航空除咗特價票之外，係包一件 15kg 寄倉行李，手提行李就包 10kg。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/26/095847_606bdf8f414e97d696c1848dcd2b13b9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F26%2F095847_606bdf8f414e97d696c1848dcd2b13b9.jpg&h=d898c6a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n六點幾飛到釜山，因為冬天日照短，降落後都未天光。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/26/095853_ff9b8cf094a1bd8d93fef2f58e2edf53.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F26%2F095853_ff9b8cf094a1bd8d93fef2f58e2edf53.jpg&h=41e5831c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n釜山換錢唔似喺首爾咁成行成市，匯價亦比較差，機場銀行換就肯定低，但市區都唔好得幾多，啲鋪頭唔會明碼實價寫匯率，要自己問。<br />\n<br />\n如果你住釜山火車站附近都仲好啲，嗰邊叫做多幾間兌換店，住海雲臺直頭得兩間可以揀，見過其中一間寫港幣 140 ，首爾名洞係換梗 145，差額都幾大。<br />\n<br />\n最後我係直接香港卡撳機，拎咗 30萬圜，計埋手續費15蚊都仲有 142 。<br />\n<br />\n最先係去釜山銀行撳，結果佢計出嚟有幾千圜手續費，就去咗呢間撳，冇手續費。<br />\n<br />\n喺入境地下嗰層望外面嘅左手邊，去到尾嘅角落頭。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/26/095850_b334fcc49bb33bc2f149b2ecf2e610ad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F26%2F095850_b334fcc49bb33bc2f149b2ecf2e610ad.jpg&h=bd723ee1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n市區就有利撚銀行（渣打），都係免手續費。<br />\n<br />\n待爛尾。"},{"pid":"d22a93e8490113021973d5a8f4f26256a563ce48","tid":914403,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2500063d72dd08c2d3d70f6f963576